gw.api.match

Class MatchableTreeTraverser

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.match.MatchableTreeTraverser

  • public class MatchableTreeTraverser
extends java.lang.Object
    MatchableTreeTraverser - Used to traverse a policy period and construct MatchableKey information. On construction, traverses the input policy period and builds:
    • MatchableKey -> KeyableBean map
    • Map of edges representing the FK relationships between traversed nodes.
    Traversal of tree is controlled through a passed in configuration object. See MatchableTreeTraverserConfig.
